This directory (build_system) contains the Makefiles that form the build system
of the KIM API package.

The contents of the directory are as follows:

Makefile.Generic
     Makefile containing common definitions for the KIM API build system

Makefile.LoadDefaults
     Makefile for loading and setting default values the KIM API build system

Makefile.Model
     Makefile containing the KIM API build system's definitions for Models

Makefile.ModelDriver
     Makefile containing the KIM API build system's definitions for Model
     Drivers

Makefile.ParameterizedModel
     Makefile containing the KIM API build system's definitions for
     Parameterized Models

Makefile.SanityCheck
     Makefile that verifies all necessary settings have been set by the user
     and that they have appropriate values

README
     This file

compiler_defaults/
     Directory containing the various standard compiler default setting values

linker_defaults/
     Directory containing the various standard linker default setting values

parameterized_model.cpp
     C++ code for creating a Parameterized Model
